Body: Description: I advised the customer to upgrade NEA to the latest version because the SharePoint Permission scan takes over 15 days and is aborted before completion. The scan used to take between 3 to 5 days to complete.

What We've Learned Updated: The customer is having a performance issue on SharePoint.
It takes over 15 days to scan SPAA (Permission scan)
The customer is on the 11.6.0.11 version
I advise the customer to upgrade to the latest version.
Next Steps Updated: Upgrade to the latest version
